Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.09,0:02:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈罗 PC模式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.44,0:03:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在干什么 菲利特？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把之前收集到的全部战斗数据
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传送给AGE系统
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好吗？凡格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.93,0:03:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 随时可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.22,0:03:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能这样啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.04,0:03:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是重要的工作之一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么工作…说得像个军人似的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.88,0:03:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺拉毁了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们今后该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.14,0:03:36.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸和妈妈 不知现在怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.91,0:03:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不然 去问舰长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:03:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古鲁迪克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.27,0:04:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有点事 想问古鲁迪克先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:07.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去问其他船员
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样 真不讨人喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 但那也是没办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长是个大忙人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们 今后会怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这艘船现在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.25,0:04:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为进行补给 正前往法丁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七天后抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说联邦军保护下的诺拉市民
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被送往托尔迪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.21,0:04:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在法丁乘坐往托尔迪亚方向的飞船就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.34,0:04:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军队会为你们准备船票
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.77,0:04:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也会试着联络你们的父母
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.62,0:04:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.68,0:04:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得事不关己似的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:47.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特不去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.13,0:04:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里到底怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.01,0:04:55.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这里不是诺拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候启航的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有过战斗是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 你们是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.58,0:05:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！ 沃尔夫·安尼克
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认识？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.46,0:05:10.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大名人呐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶机动战士的世界锦标赛 原明星选手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.57,0:05:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说加入联邦军了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:17.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来在这艘船上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下是本舰航行总管…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.14,0:05:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对男人的自我介绍不感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:28.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒想仔细听听你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.25,0:05:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.84,0:05:31.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是蜜蕾丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.28,0:05:32.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那从今往后就叫 小蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.55,0:05:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 为什么军舰上有孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里什么时候成幼儿园了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:44.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幼儿园？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些孩子是诺拉上的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:49.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为突然遭到UE袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 所以慌慌张张逃上船吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.73,0:05:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过 不是普通的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.66,0:05:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是人类中第一个击落UE的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.18,0:06:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶自己制造的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.22,0:06:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.52,0:06:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没意思的笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有骗你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.50,0:06:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 冰眠醒来就遇上这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.57,0:06:17.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这世界到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也是接到紧急命令从诺拉登舰的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,详情请去询问古鲁迪克舰长…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古鲁迪克？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁？什么时候换的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.35,0:06:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 算了 别说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我直接去问那个古鲁迪克本人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.10,0:06:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他…他是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.38,0:06:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了是沃尔夫·安尼克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界锦标赛的原明星选手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.06,0:06:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自觉高处不胜寒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.99,0:06:47.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高调入伍的性格人士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.12,0:06:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭借动物般的敏锐直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和准确无比的操纵技术
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.95,0:06:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绰号白狼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是联邦军的王牌机师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.92,0:06:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的那么了不起？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.86,0:07:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 有认真干活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位技师们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.88,0:07:20.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这就是为我准备的新机动战士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.95,0:07:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好机体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:30.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错了 这是我的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫高达
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.92,0:07:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我要了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.09,0:07:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭什么这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.59,0:07:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道我外号叫什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.34,0:07:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白狼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 白色机体就是我的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.93,0:07:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换句话说 这台叫高达的玩意儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.64,0:07:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是我的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭什么这样啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.48,0:07:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是本舰机动战士部队的队长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.24,0:08:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:02.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁…谁说的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古鲁迪克舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.12,0:08:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚得到舰长的亲自任命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以我的实力 这也在情理之中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.23,0:08:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失败的任命…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.58,0:08:20.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 高达归我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.19,0:08:20.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.28,0:08:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不满吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:24.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就比试比试
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.39,0:08:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比试？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.87,0:08:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面我和你驾驶机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进行一对一模拟战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.59,0:08:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我赢的话 高达归我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一我输的话 从此不提此事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达可不是玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.35,0:08:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道 是兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特简直把自己当成军人了 这么较真
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.61,0:08:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拒绝挑战 直接认输也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.81,0:08:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 接受你的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.13,0:08:59.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米莉 为什么擅自…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.15,0:09:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达如果被收走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就不会再把自己当作军人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来还是这位妹妹更有胆量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:11.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 小子？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.66,0:09:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 比就比！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说定了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机动战士发射口展开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.29,0:09:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达出击后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.75,0:09:23.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰诺亚斯特装型出击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:26.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好吗 舰长？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.28,0:09:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以当作训练
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出发 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达 左舷二号发射口离舰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.15,0:09:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机动战士弹射部署 入轨程序开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.13,0:09:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射控制系统与高达连接 确认
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同步加速器 一号到四号启动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.16,0:09:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,匹配完成 各项目数值正常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.91,0:09:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入轨程序开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:09:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弹射器作业人员 返回作业司令室
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气压调整系统 启动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.02,0:10:02.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甲板内气压无变化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.73,0:10:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入弹射程序
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终确认弹射路线
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射出方向上 未发现陨石小行星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二号发射口 弹射器功能正常
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离舰准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.05,0:10:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢噢 还有模有样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面 杰诺亚斯特装型
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入出击准备状态
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.33,0:10:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警戒宇域内友军机高达
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.96,0:10:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留意相对距离
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.62,0:10:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一号发射口 完成发射准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.81,0:10:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃尔夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:44.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰诺亚斯特装型 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别忘记约定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:54.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会输呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这把标记枪决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打中虽然不会造成实际伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但电脑会判定受创程度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.09,0:11:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间限制是30分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.27,0:11:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此期间命中对手越多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,点数越高的一方获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.19,0:11:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 准备战斗开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:36.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪方会赢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.85,0:11:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正常想的话是沃尔夫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 或许…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.05,0:11:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.95,0:11:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时奉陪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.93,0:11:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,READY
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,GO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:11:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:11:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊 沃尔夫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.60,0:11:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别输给他 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.99,0:12:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.40,0:12:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞄准太业余
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么 刚才是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.78,0:12:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘记说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中弹后会受到一瞬间的电击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.04,0:12:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 就算是给菜鸟的一点惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.10,0:12:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种说法… 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打不中 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.64,0:12:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去菲利特会一败涂地的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在干什么 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细观察对方的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,观察对方的行动？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.86,0:12:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 我面对UE的时候不也做到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光看着可赢不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好 干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.69,0:13:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.38,0:13:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害啊 那小子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.14,0:13:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 了不起 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 说的也不全是大话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达是我的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.42,0:13:58.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是时候动真格的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.39,0:14:02.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再好不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.30,0:14:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.51,0:14:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是UE吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.97,0:14:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达 杰诺亚斯特装型
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:24.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与疑似UE的敌人遭遇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.54,0:14:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入交战状态
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员 一级战斗配置 快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.08,0:14:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员 一级战斗配置
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一级战斗配置
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在干什么 艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.58,0:14:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 标记枪没法…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凡格斯 发射多兹步枪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.30,0:14:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白 正在准备呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.56,0:14:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:00.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你退后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃尔夫先生才是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.20,0:15:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.70,0:15:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和UE战斗过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:08.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达的话 能办到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.61,0:15:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.07,0:15:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以像诺拉时那样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用光束短剑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.98,0:15:35.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.01,0:15:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差点就干掉它了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 别说话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.62,0:15:44.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.60,0:15:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看那里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.42,0:16:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.26,0:16:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 沃尔夫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.81,0:16:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 报告情况
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.08,0:16:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…高达和杰诺亚斯特装型
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有敌人机动战士型的反应消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.60,0:16:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长 让本舰前往支援吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.30,0:16:24.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号原地待命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.57,0:16:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让这艘船贸然前往情况不明的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优先警戒周边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.46,0:16:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 爷爷？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是菲利特他们的反应消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.44,0:16:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点 艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在要相信菲利特 等着他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.04,0:16:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.73,0:16:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼下的装备 心有余而力不足
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好在似乎没有被对方发觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.25,0:17:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老老实实等它过去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.48,0:17:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知是什么道理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.36,0:17:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此靠近也无法探测到那艘巨舰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只能等了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.88,0:17:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃尔夫先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道 听我的别动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.75,0:17:39.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:46.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.07,0:17:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃尔夫先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.66,0:17:53.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回到歌姬号上去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.09,0:17:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大致位置知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.21,0:17:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.03,0:17:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是为了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.62,0:18:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉大家敌舰在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.50,0:18:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.82,0:18:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见识下吧 白狼的本事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.56,0:18:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索敌系统有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:17.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友军信号？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是高达！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:21.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接通线路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.73,0:18:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 听得见吗 请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.85,0:18:25.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜蕾丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.78,0:18:28.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射多兹步枪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.05,0:18:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还等什么 快！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.39,0:18:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凡格斯 可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.36,0:18:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 发射多兹步枪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.74,0:18:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家别过来 有敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.87,0:18:54.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数量众多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.80,0:18:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数量众多？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.54,0:18:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取道高达所在的航线
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.43,0:19:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这趟好像玩大了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.69,0:19:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.47,0:19:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.06,0:19:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.40,0:20:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通知歌姬号了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.69,0:20:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 这个数量…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.33,0:20:14.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.48,0:21:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消…消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.02,0:21:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不明白是怎么回事 看来得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.97,0:21:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 沃尔夫先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.45,0:21:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也蛮能干的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:35.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 坏成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.03,0:21:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不替我们这些修理的人想想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.88,0:21:41.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了 听说这次特别危险
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.05,0:21:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机师次次都是在玩命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.08,0:21:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了没事！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.11,0:21:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真能说 差点就哭出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.22,0:21:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时我就说了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.63,0:21:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是男人就别放弃 还有机会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.02,0:21:58.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明没说过 这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.02,0:22:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说我把情况告诉歌姬号以后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.74,0:22:03.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了救沃尔夫先生才回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.69,0:22:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在听吗 沃尔夫先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:13.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来敌人有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.66,0:22:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不被雷达和光学传感器探知的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.70,0:22:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不见的伞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.28,0:22:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渐渐有眉目了 UE的真相
